  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mixolumia is an entrancing falling block arcade puzzler where diamond blocks slide together on a gem-shaped board and explode in glittering chain reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scintillating visuals and entrancing music that responds and evolves with your actions make Mixolumia a chill experience for casual players or an adrenaline rush for  hardcore puzzle fiends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Swap the Soundtrack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each included song has unique sound effects that harmonize with the music, giving the game a totally different feel depending on which track you choose.</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/75aad9dbbf02b150fdbab19a0a0073af.poster.avif?t=1767400537\" width=294 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/75aad9dbbf02b150fdbab19a0a0073af.webm?t=1767400537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remix the Colors</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch up Mixolumia's visuals by selecting from a wide range of lovely color palettes, or create and customize your own with the built-in color editor.</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/d1d7bf9a8d7881dfab8090556c64a05e.poster.avif?t=1767400537\" width=416 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/d1d7bf9a8d7881dfab8090556c64a05e.webm?t=1767400537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you want to chill out, or challenge yourself to intense, strategic gameplay, Mixolumia has a game mode to suit your mood.</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/3aea5f4456b83cfcd87353c96bd44ca1.poster.avif?t=1767400537\" width=528 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/3aea5f4456b83cfcd87353c96bd44ca1.webm?t=1767400537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mixolumia has options to adjust or turn off all of its effects individually so as to be as accessible to players as possible.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Honors</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/3e242386479059a865675f31004d7fab.avif?t=1767400537\" width=560 height=296 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mixolumia is an entrancing falling block arcade puzzler where diamond blocks slide together on a gem-shaped board and explode in glittering chain reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scintillating visuals and entrancing music that responds and evolves with your actions make Mixolumia a chill experience for casual players or an adrenaline rush for  hardcore puzzle fiends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Swap the Soundtrack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each included song has unique sound effects that harmonize with the music, giving the game a totally different feel depending on which track you choose.</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/75aad9dbbf02b150fdbab19a0a0073af.poster.avif?t=1767400537\" width=294 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/75aad9dbbf02b150fdbab19a0a0073af.webm?t=1767400537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remix the Colors</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch up Mixolumia's visuals by selecting from a wide range of lovely color palettes, or create and customize your own with the built-in color editor.</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/d1d7bf9a8d7881dfab8090556c64a05e.poster.avif?t=1767400537\" width=416 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/d1d7bf9a8d7881dfab8090556c64a05e.webm?t=1767400537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you want to chill out, or challenge yourself to intense, strategic gameplay, Mixolumia has a game mode to suit your mood.</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/3aea5f4456b83cfcd87353c96bd44ca1.poster.avif?t=1767400537\" width=528 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/3aea5f4456b83cfcd87353c96bd44ca1.webm?t=1767400537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mixolumia has options to adjust or turn off all of its effects individually so as to be as accessible to players as possible.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Honors</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414020/extras/3e242386479059a865675f31004d7fab.avif?t=1767400537\" width=560 height=296 /></span>",
